data.title: Fills a need
data.text: This place is always busy.  I have always had good, friendly service.  Never had a messed up order.  I always order to go, and it is ready before I finish paying.  Food is always fresh and hot.  They always accommodate if I need to make a substitution.  This is combined with AW, so there are some options other than chicken.  Obviously this isn't fine dining, but for KFC this is a good one.

data.title: Worst meal I've ever had
data.text:
We went through drive through and ordered two three-piece all white meals with cole slaw sides.  The only good thing was the cole slaw.  The clerk misheard and thought  we said two piece - I ordered grilled - I got a little tiny breast and a wing that looks like they had sat in the restaurant for hours.  It was our fault for not double checking, but KFC needs to step up and do a better job with their food.

I will never go back to KFC if it's the only place on earth
